                        "content": "The nurse is assessing a client experiencing an exacerbation of irritable bowel syndrome (IBS) who is experiencing localized abdominal pain. The nurse prepares to perform abdominal palpation, knowing which of the following abdominal quadrants would most likely elicit tenderness with palpation due to this condition?",
